'''Andy Amadi Okoroafor numukinnyi''' wa firime [[Nijeriya|wo]] muri [[Nijeriya|Nigeriya]] nkumuvugizi wa TED<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/andy-amadi-okoroafor/</ref>.  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa film ya ''Relentless ya'' 2010.  Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni umwanditsi, producer numuyobozi wubuhanzi. Niwe washinze sitidiyo yo guhanga 'Clam'<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm4162175/</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 8 Gashyantare 1966 i Bauchi, mu majyaruguru ya [[Nijeriya]]. Yari afite umwaka umwe igihe intambara yatangiraga i Biafra<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/270472677_Okoroafor_Andy_Amadi_Relentless_2010_95_min_With_Gideon_Okeke_Nneka_Egbuna_and_Jimmy_Jean-Louis_France_and_Nigeria_English_Clam_Films_No_price_reported</ref>. Nyuma yaje kwimukira i Paris mu [[Bufaransa]] maze akora nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe ubuhanzi mu kwamamaza, imideli n'amashusho y'indirimbo. Ni na TED-Mugenzi<ref>https://blog.ted.com/fellows-friday-with-andy-amadi-okoroafor/</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu [[Bufaransa]], Okoroafor yamaze imyaka 5 yubuhanzi ayobora amashusho yindirimbo <ref>https://clamfilms2.wordpress.com/andy-okoroafor/</ref>, kuva kuri alubumu kugeza ku mashusho yindirimbo. Yashinze sitidiyo yo guhanga yitwa 'Clam' na 'Clam magazine' mu 1999.  Iki kinyamakuru gisohoka kabiri mu mwaka mu [[Buyapani]], [[Amerika]], [[Uburayi]], na [[Berezile]]<ref>https://www.xyz.ng/en/people/andy-amadi-okoroafor-biography-fact-career-awards-net-worth-and-life-story-102598</ref>.  Mu imurikagurisha rya 2017, yayoboye igitaramo ''show Never Surrender'', i M. Bassy i Hamburg, mu [[Budage]]. Muri iki gitaramo harimo gufotora no kwerekana amashusho murukurikirane, ''Aphrike Yinshi''<ref>https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/african-studies-review/article/andy-amadi-okoroafor-relentless-2010-95-min-with-gideon-okeke-nneka-egbuna-and-jimmy-jeanlouis-france-and-nigeria-english-clam-films-no-price-reported/AF4AE386A7D6EEE44E781FFB6953395A</ref> . Hamwe nuruhererekane, yakoranye na mugenzi we bafotora hamwe nuwakoze firime, Andrew Dosunmu.<ref>https://m-bassy.org/en/programm/more-aphrike-2</ref> 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, Okoroafor yakoze filime ''Relentless'', filime ye ya mbere.  Mu Kwakira 2010, iyi filime yatoranijwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ryabereye i Londres, ryerekanwa ku ya 6 Ukuboza 2010 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Afurika ryabereye i Port Harcourt ku nshuro ya mbere muri [[Afurika]]<ref>http://kalamu.com/neogriot/2013/10/08/interview-video-andy-amadi-okoroafor/</ref><ref>https://www.filmlinc.org/films/relentless/</ref>. 

